  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomized phase II trial will compare the efficacy and toxicity of Gemcitabine plus
      Erlotinib versus Gemcitabine plus Erlotinib plus Oxaliplatin in patients with pancreatic
      cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
